dc_title_s: Map of the Ottoman dominions in Asia: with the adjacent frontiers of the Russian and Persian Empires; Published by Jas. Wyld, Charring Cross East. Geographer to Her Majesty, 1843.
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures. Includes notes. Shows routes of Cyrus and Xenophon, and of Napoleonic military campaigns. 1 map: hand col., dissected and mounted on linen; 52 x 73 cm., folded 19 x 10 cm.
